Package: DDFConverter
Type: Package
Title: Convert a dataset into a DDF-filesystem
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Amelia Bodin
Maintainer: Amelia Bodin <amelia.bodin@statistikkonsulterna.se>
Description: This R-package uses an existing dataset and easily transforms into a DDF-filesystem, which can be used in the Vizabi tool.
    Four functions are included; 
    create_concepts creates only the concepts-file. 
    create_entities creates only the entities-file.
    create_datapoints creates only datapoint-files. 
    create_ddf creates an entire filesystem containing concepts, entities and datapoints.
    NOTE: A datapackage-generator is not included. To validate your DDF-filesystem use the built-in validator in the Gapminder Offline-tool, or the terminal.
    More info on validating here: https://github.com/Gapminder/ddf-validation.
